Trade/Device Name(s): CLINIQA Liquid QC™ Bilirubin Controls Levels 1, 2 & 3
CLINIQA LiniCAL™ Bilirubin Calibration Verifiers Levels A-E for Olympus AU Systems™
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for CLINIQA Liquid QC Bilirubin Controls and LiniCAL Bilirubin Calibration Verifiers for Olympus AU Systems as assayed quality control materials.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended as assayed quality control materials to provide levels of Total and Direct Bilirubin and to evaluate performance of Olympus AU Systems at various concentrations.
